----------------------------
Running example

1 Paired-end ChIP-seq dataset

cd PE_demo
SNVAS PEsample_peaks_sorted.bed PEsample_peaks_sorted.bam PEcontrol_peaks_sorted.bam PEsample.vcf

Filtering process:
SNVAS_filter PEsample.vcf 20 homo 10 PEsample_homo.vcf
SNVAS_filter PEsample.vcf 20 hetero 100 PEsample_heter.vcf
SNVAS_filter PEsample.vcf 20 hetero_AS 100 PEsample_heterAS.vcf
SNVAS_filter PEsample.vcf 20 hetero_nonAS 100 PEsample_heterNonAS.vcf

2 Single-end ChIP-seq dataset

cd SE_demo
SNVAS SEsample_peaks_sorted.bed SEsample_peaks_sorted.bam SEcontrol_peaks_sorted.bam SEsample.vcf

Filtering process:
SNVAS_filter SEsample.vcf 20 homo 10 SEsample_homo.vcf
SNVAS_filter SEsample.vcf 20 hetero 100 SEsample_heter.vcf
SNVAS_filter SEsample.vcf 20 hetero_AS 100 SEsample_heterAS.vcf
SNVAS_filter SEsample.vcf 20 hetero_nonAS 100 SEsample_heterNonAS.vcf

